WEBVTT

00:11:57.066 --> 00:12:03.500
(Applause)

00:12:08.811 --> 00:12:09.961
(Applause ends)

00:12:10.684 --> 00:12:14.783
For me, it's about being present
and really listening.

00:12:15.382 --> 00:12:18.549
Dependents want to feel
a part of something, anything.

00:12:18.573 --> 00:12:22.065
It doesn't need to be something
exceptionally profound that's shared --

00:12:23.041 --> 00:12:25.302
it could be as simple as walks together.

00:12:26.635 --> 00:12:28.658
Give them a voice

00:12:29.262 --> 00:12:32.558
of interaction, participation,